Package: townofcary.org
Title: Town of Cary NC Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Town of Cary, NC open data portal (Opendatasoft API v2). Covers dataset discovery, record retrieval, CSV export, and convenience wrappers for police incidents, restaurants, and developments. Includes LLM context injection via cary_context().
